interviewer(p1): you have worked in synapse,what can you tell me about it.
Synapse committee member(p2): there are many events which take place in synapse, i personally worked in conducting  the quizzing event.
It was a theme based event with a harry-potter theme. The gifts for the winners were provided by sponsors. We had planned to conduct 2 levels of quizzes. 
If there were a draw between any groups we would have looked at the time taken by each group and decided the winner based on it. 
