p1: Do you remember any challenges you faced in Synapse?
P2 : some members are stationed on the gate for registering on-spot registrations. It becomes hectic as there are many people coming on event day.
CONCLUSIONS:
Different events must not be mixed, their information must be stored separately, on the spot registrations can’t be closed as maximum participation is encouraged,
online registration must be encouraged as much as possible.
Also different sponsor’s data must be stored.

